.NET Framework 3.5.name: SDK_BaseController
.NET Framework 3.5.summary: The Base Controller SDK script provides a bridge to SDK methods that deal with the input devices.
.NET Framework 3.5.remarks: This is an abstract class to implement the interface required by all implemented SDKs.
